description: Torquay United sign 20-year-old Derby County forward Emmanuel Ilesanmi on loan.
title: Emmanuel Ilesanmi: Torquay United sign Derby County forward on loan
title_page: Emmanuel Ilesanmi: Torquay United sign Derby County forward on loan - BBC Sport
maintext:
Torquay United have signed Derby County forward Emmanuel Ilesanmi on loan.
The 20-year-old has agreed an initial one-month deal at the National League South promotion chasers.
He has scored four goals in eight Premier League 2 appearances for the Rams so far this season, having moved to the Championship side from League Two Harrogate Town last summer.
